(224, 'us', 'Climbing hold bolt', '<p>Durable steel climbing hold bolt with hex socket, suitable for indoor climbing wall installations.</p>\n', '<p>Ensure secure and stable attachment of climbing holds with this high-quality climbing hold bolt. Crafted from durable steel, it features a hex socket design, allowing for easy installation and removal using an Allen wrench. This bolt is ideal for use with T-nuts in wooden panels, providing a reliable fastening solution for both indoor and outdoor climbing walls.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Material:</strong> High-strength steel for enhanced durability.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Design:</strong> Hex socket head for easy tightening and loosening.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Compatibility:</strong> Designed for use with T-nuts in wooden climbing panels.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Finish:</strong> Corrosion-resistant coating to withstand various environmental conditions.</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Whether you&#39;re setting up a new climbing wall or upgrading an existing one, this climbing hold bolt offers the reliability and performance you need.</p>\n', NULL, '2021-08-26 15:19:14', '2025-06-20 18:03:19'),
(225, 'us', 'Hold 15', '<p>Hold 15</p>', '<p>Hold 15</p>', NULL, '2021-08-26 15:27:18', '2021-08-26 15:30:29'),
(226, 'us', 'Hold 16', '<p>Hold 16</p>\n', '<p>Hold 16</p>\n', NULL, '2021-08-26 15:30:50', '2024-04-08 20:33:51'),
(227, 'us', 'Hold 17', '<p>Hold 17</p>\n', '<p>Hold 17</p>\n', NULL, '2021-08-26 15:37:50', '2024-04-08 20:35:02'),
(228, 'us', 'T-nuts', '<p>Zinc-plated 4-prong T-Nuts for secure attachment of climbing holds on wooden panels.</p>\n', '<p>Ensure a stable and durable climbing wall setup with these high-quality T-Nuts. Crafted from zinc-plated steel, they feature a 4-prong design that securely anchors into wooden panels, preventing rotation and providing a reliable base for your climbing holds.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Material:</strong> Zinc-plated steel for enhanced durability and corrosion resistance.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Design:</strong> 4-prong configuration ensures a firm grip in wood panels.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Compatibility:</strong> Designed for use with standard climbing hold bolts.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Installation:</strong> Easily hammered into pre-drilled holes for quick setup.</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Ideal for both indoor and outdoor climbing walls, these T-Nuts are a must-have for route setters and climbing enthusiasts looking to build or upgrade their climbing setups.</p>\n', NULL, '2021-08-26 15:41:06', '2025-06-20 17:52:26'),
