(241, 'us', 'Chalk bag', '<p>Durable and practical chalk bag with a wide opening and comfortable strap.</p>\n', '<p>A chalk bag is an essential accessory for climbers, keeping hands dry and improving grip.<br />\nThe bag is made from durable material and features a wide opening for easy chalk access.<br />\nAn adjustable strap ensures a comfortable and secure fit.<br />\nSome models may include extra pockets for storing personal items.</p>\n', NULL, '2022-02-07 21:09:14', '2025-06-20 17:47:18'),
(242, 'us', 'Climbing rope bag', '<p>Spacious, durable rope bag with shoulder strap and separate gear compartment&mdash;ideal for climb organization.</p>\n', '<p>Keep your climbing ropes and gear neatly organized and protected with this rugged rope bag. Made from tough ripstop nylon, it features a wide zippered opening for easy rope packing and retrieval. A padded shoulder strap and reinforced grab handle make transport effortless, whether you&#39;re heading to the gym or crag.</p>\n\n<p>Inside, a dedicated compartment lets you separate quickdraws, chalk, or personal items, while mesh side pockets keep snacks or water within reach. The water-resistant base helps guard contents from damp surfaces on rock ledges or gym floors.</p>\n\n<p>Lightweight yet built to last, this rope bag is a versatile must‑have for climbers seeking organization, convenience, and durability on every climb.</p>\n', NULL, '2022-02-07 21:13:35', '2025-06-20 17:43:29'),
(243, 'us', 'Belay Glasses', '<p>Prismatic belay glasses&mdash;relieve neck strain, widen view, include case and strap for climbers.</p>\n', '<p>Take care of your neck while belaying with these prismatic belay glasses. Featuring triangular prisms that redirect your view, they let you look straight ahead while watching your climber above&mdash;keeping you comfortable and focused.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Ergonomic comfort</strong>: Soft rubber or polycarbonate frames rest gently on the nose, reducing pressure during long belays .</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Durable prisms</strong>: High-quality BK7 or glass prisms resist impact, ensuring sharp, undistorted vision even after repeated use.</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Full visibility</strong>: Central prism view keeps climber in sight; peripheral vision ensures awareness of surroundings and rope position&nbsp;</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Complete kit</strong>: Includes hard case (often with carabiner), soft pouch, safety strap, and cleaning cloth for on-the-go protection and maintenance&nbsp;</p>\n	</li>\n	<li>\n	<p><strong>Better belaying = better climbing</strong>: By eliminating &quot;belayer&rsquo;s neck,&quot; you stay attentive and responsive&mdash;improving safety and focus during climbs&nbsp;</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Ideal for long gym sessions, lead belays, or multi-pitch routes, these belay glasses are a smart investment in comfort and safety. After a short adjustment period, many climbers say they&rsquo;ll never belay without them</p>\n', NULL, '2022-02-07 21:34:23', '2025-06-20 17:41:09'),
(244, 'us', 'Home exercise stand', '<p>Home exercise stand</p>', '<p>The home exercise stand is made to order. For details please contact us.</p>', NULL, '2022-03-01 20:33:31', '2022-03-01 20:47:26'),
