(66, 'us', 'Myinvartsveri ascent toure', '<p>.</p>\n', '<p>Day 1) Transfer from the Tbilisi to Stepantsminda staying 1 night in Stepantsminda and we check peoples gear and if someone need some gear we will rent it on local rent company. Day 2) Start hiking from Stepantsminda to &quot;Betlemi hut&quot;. (It is hard to make a reservation on &quot;Betlemi hat&quot; because there is not a normal reservation system. If some rooms will be free it is possible to stay inside. In other case need to stay in a tent.) Day 3) Next day we make little hike for acclimatization from the hut to the sm</p>\n', '6 Days ', '.', NULL, NULL);
